I remember something about baby monitors, but it&#39;s been too long. I see them for sale in the thrift stores though. Guess it would kinda act like a Spiricom, where an RF signal is transmitted a short distance and the entities re-modulate it. What about using one to transmit the audio from a box? 

 F-S



